
For instructions on setting up your smbpasswd file, see:

/usr/doc/samba-2.0.3/docs/textdocs/ENCRYPTION.txt

If you're having trouble connecting from Win95 and Win98 clients, you might
need to edit to client registry to use plain text passwords.  See this
file for details:

/usr/doc/samba-2.0.3/docs/textdocs/Win95.txt

